Since 1842, Fechheimer has been manufacturing quality uniforms to serve working men and women; specifically in the military and law enforcement communities. Today, Fechheimer is proud to be a Berkshire Hathaway company offering three brands; Flying Cross®, Vertx® and Justin FR™ to serve those who serve.  Our goal is to bring to market premier products and programs to continue our tradition of providing superior product & service through innovation and technology that continually meets and exceeds our customers’ expectations. If you would like to be a part of our team please review the listings by following the link below 
