We pride ourselves in our commitment to our values of Integrity, Quality & Service, Entrepreneurship, Collaboration and Accountability. In addition to salary with offer a comprehensive benefits package, and a relaxed work environment.For more information about our line of products, please visit www.flyingcross.com, www.vertx.com and www.justinfr.comFechheimer is an Equal Opportunity Employer Minorities/Females/Disabled/Veterans














