            Established in 1842, Fechheimer Brothers Company manufactures a range of uniforms for working men and women. The company provides a variety of outerwear, shirts and trousers. It offers sweaters, jackets, coats and pants. The company also provides reversible headwear, raincoats, dickeys and bike patrol uniforms. It has manufacturing partners in South America, Europe, Africa and Asia. The company offers products under the Flying Cross brand. In partnership with Head Lites Corporation, it provides Pro Series, which is a tactical safety vest. The company serves customers in the public safety, postal, military and transportation markets. Fechheimer Brothers Company is a part of Berkshire Hathaway.
          






















